  <front>
    <title>Characterization of Proposed Standards</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-kolkman-proposed-standards-clarified-05"/>
    <author initials="O." surname="Kolkman" fullname="Olaf Kolkman"/>
    <author initials="S. O." surname="Bradner" fullname="Scott O. Bradner"/>
    <author initials="S." surname="Turner" fullname="Sean Turner"/>
    <date day="31" month="October" year="2013"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   RFC 2026 describes the review performed by the IESG on IETF Proposed
   Standard RFCs and characterizes the maturity level of those
   documents.  This document updates RFC 2026 by providing a current and
   more accurate characterization of Proposed Standards.
	 </t>
